{"tid":1285264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家係有確實證據之前唔好再轉發昨天輕生的事件","createTime":"2019-07-04T13:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T14:19:32.000Z","uid":260078,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b15db938bd0e60778806ba394402e21d75f342a","tid":1285264,"uid":260078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:30:40.000Z","msg":"原po在此<br />\n<br />\n我們會代替妳走下去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284882</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n首先對於昨天離世既人感到很惋惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而基於尊重死者既前提下，<br />\n我地更加要搞清楚原樓主提供既相片係未真係黎自死者，而現在係未有確實證據證明呢樣野。<br />\n<br />\n因為愈多義士以死相練的話，會令而加本身情緒低落既人更加灰心，情緒更不穩定，引發更大既低氣壓。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n我地真係一個都不能再少，懇請大家保持頭腦清醒，比多啲時間搞清楚先轉發出去，將對大眾既傷害減到最低。</span>"},{"pid":"b73e510b1be310a7def93ab8d9b30b47aae7750c","tid":1285264,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72992dcff12d776b0437e9309bc046c1991029d6","tid":1285264,"uid":260078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1205ee566ce6b83456e0388573143172e16dbc2c","tid":1285264,"uid":260078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d93f74b59de70667ae98346d830bb169ea0cae","tid":1285264,"uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":0